    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a super-affordable way to get on the road? This car is a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper! While it needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its prime, it\u2019s a great starting point for anyone who loves to roll up their sleeves. Priced specifically to reflect its current state, this is your chance to snag a bargain and make it your own!",
